Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting old words\Nthat have been used up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to convey\Nmy simple thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day's faint wind blows away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the castle ruins of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh with you\Nand live for the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still that incident\Nwill continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it must be good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving nothing behind,\Nlet us share what is left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, we'll realize\Nthat it was everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sadness will touch our cheeks,\Ncreating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex\Nand melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got sand in my mouth…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn’t be able to do\Nanything in your current state…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy attacks with bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he does things like shoot bones\Nand extrude bones from inside his body…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He controls bones freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara of the Desert…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use sand,\Nas the name implies, huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara vs. Kimimaro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough defense using sand…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He…isn’t a close-range combat type…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting close would be difficult, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Digital Shrapnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no waste in his movements…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough,\Nhe’s a considerable Taijutsu user.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack and defense are one…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He attacks and defends\Nwith sand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the amount of sand\Nhe can control is probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…about the amount of sand\Ninside the gourd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara of the Desert…\NA dopey nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t do anything\Nif you don’t have sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the trouble of walking around\Ncarrying heavy sand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the very proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Shower…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How trite…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have sand,\NI can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who’s dopey…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s easy for me to do things\Nlike create sand with dirt…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his own sand he grinds things\Nlike rocks and minerals in dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and makes it into sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was sending his own sand\Nbeneath the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and adding new sand, huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara of the Desert…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His nickname isn’t just for display.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Burial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m reminded of that man\Nwhen I look at that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had the same eyes\Nas that guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to verify the value\Nof one’s own existence…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re here, aren’t you?!\NAt least answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t hate the darkness…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness is where\NI was brought up…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I…in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really God…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is, why confine me\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter who I am…\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimimaro, the time has come to use you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our sake,\Nfor the Kaguya Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… To fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only thing I can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s quite some pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would’ve been flattened\Njust like that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had I not made a membrane\Nof bone just below the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bones…That guy’s a monster, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a troublesome body, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I won’t be caught by\Nyour sand anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow… It’s beyond\Nthe scope of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,escaping from the sand\Nor not getting caught…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think it would change\Nthe terrain itself…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Sand Burial!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He’s so strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s gotten even stronger\Nthan when he fought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…this time for sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a persistent guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still…alive…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then… There’s still significance\Nfor me to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, we’re going\Nto launch a night attack
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Hidden Mist Village…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they are disconcerted\Nfrom that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the perfect time for us\Nto make them realize our ferocity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make them realize the ferocity\Nof the Kaguya Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yeah! 					– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing, Kimimaro?\NGet going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t need to think\Ndeeply about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go down to the Hidden Mist Village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kill every last person\Nyou encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just act on your instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you of the Hidden Mist Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see… Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…no. It’s nothing, Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t have time to be stopping.\NLet’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had the same eyes as I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I met Zabuza…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a hasty one, aren’t you?\NI’m not from this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you are after is right there…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have begun…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaguya Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools who can only find\Ntheir own path of life by fighting…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a simple-minded group that\Njust enjoyed slaughtering was acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a governed organization\Nas an opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they just become fools\Nrushing towards death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they fight only with power…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we the only survivors…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we’re surrounded…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense was tighter\Nthan we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’s come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take along with you\Nevery person you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll have them entertain us\Nas much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I fight for…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing anything,\NI just kept on fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come to use you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m needed…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only thing\Nthat got my body moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also able to figure out that…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t live if I didn’t fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dawn broke…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I learned that…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I myself was the only one\Nto survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I’m all alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By myself, I just wandered\Naimlessly from place to place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower, from back then…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you blooming\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won’t you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re ignoring me, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way you’d be seen\Nby someone in a place like this, yet you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe…there’s no significance to living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you might be able to\Ndiscover something interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by continuing to live…right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how you discovered that flower…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how I discovered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Let’s go…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then…\NLord Orochimaru said that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are born with\Nsome kind of significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I think…\Nsome kind of important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to protect Lord Orochimaru\Nand his ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s…that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Sasuke!\NEveryone’s worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…\Nlt’s so dark I can’t see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got better eyes than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke is in the darkness now…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Neji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be unable to catch up\Nwith Sasuke
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you stop in a place like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… You’re right!\NThis isn’t the time to stop.
